@startuml MisionFinOps
hide empty description

[*] --> pending : Mision creada

pending --> in_progress : Roles IAM adjuntados

in_progress --> partial_complete : Algunos proyectos completados
in_progress --> complete : Todos los proyectos completados (quick)
in_progress --> failed : Error irrecuperable
in_progress --> rolled_back : Rollback manual

partial_complete --> waiting_reduction : Roles mission reducidos
complete --> waiting_reduction : Roles mission reducidos

waiting_reduction --> monitoring : Mision ongoing activada
monitoring --> degraded : Health check fallido
degraded --> monitoring : Health check recuperado

failed --> [*]
rolled_back --> [*]
monitoring --> [*] : Mision cancelada

@enduml
